node.text: If you told me a lobster could convey so much emotion it would move me to tears I would’ve laughed but here we are!!! node.text:
It was such an honour to be invited back to the SNL stage for their last show of 2020. Felt so lucky to be rounding off my year with these performances and for SNL to have had me on for a skit too!! Watching everyone work and the magic behind it will be something i’ll never forget. Kristen Wiig and the whole cast were so cool and i’m still floating from all the energy 🤍 Thank you Lorne, Brian and Mel for all of your support. Thank you to my team who really are the best best BEST!!! 

Styling: @lorenzoposocco
Hair: @annacofone
Makeup: @Samanthalmua
Nails: @NailsByMei

Creative: @ceremony.london 
Musical director: @williambowerman
Choreography: @CharmLaDonna
Dancers: @Aclark_4 @nataly__santiago 
@robynwilliams_ @audreydouglass
Band: @dbxsupreme @guitarianna @grantzubritsky

Thank you @permpressmedia @julianrupert @nawalalalalal
